nal de la Route\n: 2nd Trofeo Baracchi (with [[Bernard Guyot]])\n: 2nd Crit\u00e9rium des As\n: 3rd Overall [[1967 Giro d'Italia|Giro d'Italia]]\n: 7th Overall Giro di Sardegna\n;1968\n: 1st Trofeo Baracchi (with [[Felice Gimondi]])\n: 4th [[1968 Li\u00e8ge\u2013Bastogne\u2013Li\u00e8ge|Li\u00e8ge\u2013Bastogne\u2013Li\u00e8ge]]\n: 5th Crit\u00e9rium des As\n: 10th Overall [[1968 Paris\u2013Nice|Paris\u2013Nice]]\n;1969\n: 1st [[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px]] Overall [[1969 Tour of the Basque Country|Tour of the Basque Country]]\n: 3rd Overall [[1969 Paris\u2013Nice|Paris\u2013Nice]]\n: 4th Overall [[1969 Crit\u00e9rium du Dauphin\u00e9 Lib\u00e9r\u00e9|Crit\u00e9rium du Dauphin\u00e9 Lib\u00e9r\u00e9]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Grand Tour results timeline===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|\n! scope=\"col\" | 1957\n! scope=\"col\" | 1958\n! scope=\"col\" | 1959\n! scope=\"col\" | 1960\n! scope=\"col\" | 1961\n! scope=\"col\" | 1962\n! scope=\"col\" | 1963\n! scope=\"col\" | 1964\n! scope=\"col\" | 1965\n! scope=\"col\" | 1966\n! scope=\"col\" | 1967\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[1962 Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a|DNF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:yellow;\"|[[1963 Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a|'''1''']]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Giro d'Italia]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2013\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ddf;\"|[[1959 Giro d'Italia|'''2''']]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:pink|[[1960 Giro d'Italia|'''1''']]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ddf;\"|[[1961 Giro d'Italia|'''2''']]\n| style=\"text-al