 but the record was never ratified by the UCI following Anquetil's refusal to take a post race doping control, and on 13 October the UCI voted not to allow the record.{{sfn|Howard|2008|pp=209\u2212217}}}}\n|}\n\n=== Awards ===\n* [[BBC Overseas Sports Personality of the Year]]: 1963<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/in_depth/2000/sports_personality/1039150.stm|title=Protopopov and who?|work=[[BBC Sport]]|publisher=BBC|date=25 November 2000|first=Robin|last=Scott-Elliot|accessdate=16 October 2015}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[List of doping cases in cycling]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n== Bibliography ==\n* {{cite book | last=Fournel | first=Paul | author-link=Paul Fournel | title=Anquetil, Alone: The legend of the controversial Tour de France champion | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_n3ZDQAAQBAJ | year=2017 | publisher=[[Profile Books]] | location=London | isbn=978-1-78283-298-0 }}\n* {{cite book | ref=harv | last=Howard | first=Paul | title=Sex, Lies and Handlebar Tape: The Remarkable Life of Jacques Anquetil, the First Five-Times Winner of the Tour de France | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=v0eNTAHzlyEC | year=2008 | publisher=[[Mainstream Publishing]] | location=Edinburgh | isbn=978-1-84596-301-9 }}\n* {{cite book | ref=harv | last=Yates | first=Richard | title=Master Jacques: The Enigma of Jacques Anquetil | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LixaNQAACAAJ | year=2001 | publisher=Mousehold Press | location=Norwich, UK | isbn=978-1-874739-18-0 }}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{cycling archives|245|Jacques Anquetil}}\n* {{cite web|title=Results page Jacques Anquetil (France)|url=https://www.cyclingranking.com/rider/2519/jacques-anquetil|work=cyclingranking.com}}\n\n{{S-start|header={{s-ach|rec}}}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Fausto Coppi]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Hour record|UCI hour record]] (46.159 km)| years = 29 June 1956 \u2013 19 September 1956}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ercole Baldini]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Tour de France Yellow Jersey}}\n{{maglia rosa}}\n{{Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a winners}}\n{{Li\u00e8ge\u2013Bastogne\u2013Li\u00e8ge winners}}\n{{Super Prestige Pernod International winners}}{{UCI Hall of Fame}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Anquetil, Jacques}}\n[[Category:1934 births]]\n[[Category:1987 deaths]]\n[[Category:Chevaliers of the L\u00e9gion d'honneur]]\n[[Category:Cyclists at the 1952 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cancer in France]]\n[[Category:Deaths from stomach cancer]]\n[[Category:Doping cases in cycling]]\n[[Category:French Giro d'Italia stage winners]]\n[[Category:French male cyclists]]\n[[Category:French Tour de France stage winners]]\n[[Category:French Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a stage winners]]\n[[Category:Giro d'Italia cyclists]]\n[[Category:Giro d'Italia winners]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1952 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France]]\n[[Category:Olympic cyclists of France]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in cycling]]\n[[Category:People from Mont-Saint-Aignan]]\n[[Category:People from Normandy]]\n[[Category:Tour de France cyclists]]\n[[Category:Tour de France winners]]\n[[Category:Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a cyclists]]\n[[Category:Vuelta a Espa\u00f1a winners]]\n[[Category:Giro d'Italia and Tour de France winners in the same year]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Seine-Maritime]]\n[[Category:BBC Sports Personality World Sport Star of the Year winners]]\n", "name_user": "Lepricavark", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:added short description", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Anquetil"}
{"title_page": "Rasoolpur Soor", "text_new": "[[File:Rasoolpur Soor's some memorable pictures|thumb|I miss my village too much]]\n{{multiple issues|\n{{Orphan|date=February 2014}}\n{{unreferenced|date=February 2014}}\n}}\n\n<!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Indian cities]] for details -->\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Rasoolpur Soor\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = Hindi,Urdu & Rasoolpuri\n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Village\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Uttar Pradesh#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Uttar Pradesh, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|27.43|N|82.18|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Uttar Pradesh]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Balrampur district|Balrampur]]\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = Parliamentary Seat \n| governing_body          = Shravasti\n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          =\n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_total       = \n| population_as_of        = \n| population_rank         = \n| population_density_km2  = \n| population_demonym      = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| demographics_type1      = Languages\n| demographics1_title1    = Official\n| demographics1_info1     = [[Hindi language|Hindi]]\n| timezone1               = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1             = \n| postal_code_type        = <!-- [[Postal Index Number|PIN]] -->\n| postal_code             = \n| registration_plate      = \n| blank1_name_sec1        = \n| blank1_info_sec1        = \n| website                 = {{url|http://www.balrampur.nic.in}}\n| footnotes               = \n}}\n\n[[(Rasoolpur Soor)]] is a village in [[Balrampur district]] of [[Uttar Pradesh]], India. It is situated on the bank of the Pipra Talab [[(Ponds)]] half of the Pipra Talab occupied by Rasoolpur Soor from a long. In this village there are 115 separate hoses with a population of 800 people. The people of this village title them selves with SooRi, there's an own history behind this title.The current Head of the village (Gram Pradhan) is Mr. Bakridi Khan and Block Head Mr. Sageer Alam Khan also belongs to this village.\n\nLast but not the least, Software Engineer Mr. [[Mohammad Shadab Ahmad Khan]] informed us that people of this village are living very merely with fraternity.They are an example to prove \"Unity is strength\".There's a Mosque in middle of the village, that's highlight the beauty of the village.\n\n'''About''' [[(Rasoolpur Soor) including Nabi Nagar]] : \n\nAccording to Census 2011 information the location code or village code of Rasoolpur Soor village is 173873. Rasoolpur Soor village is located in Utraula Tehsil of Balrampur district in Uttar Pradesh, India. It is situated 8km away from sub-district headquarter Utraula and 39km away from district headquarter Balrampur.As per 2009 stats, Rassolpur is the gram panchayat of Rasoolpur Soor village.The total geographical area of village is 144.06 hectares.Rasoolpur Soor has a total population of 1,529 peoples. There are about 193 houses in Rasoolpur Soor village.  Utraula is nearest town to Rasoolpur Soor which is approximately 8km away.\n\n'''Rasoolpur Soor Population in the form of percent(approximate)'''\nThe percentage of male population is 52.26%.\nThe percentage of female population is 47.74%.\nThe percentage of child population is 17.99%.\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Balrampur district]]\n\n\n{{Balrampur-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "[[File:Rasoolpur Soor's some memorable pictures|thumb|I miss my village too much]]\n{{multiple issues|\n{{Orphan|date=February 2014}}\n{{unreferenced|date=February 2014}}\n}}\n\n<!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Indian cities]] for details -->\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Rasoolpur Soor\n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = Hindi,Urdu & Rasoolpuri\n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Village\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Uttar Pradesh#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Uttar Pradesh, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|27.43|N|82.18|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [[States and territories of India|State]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Uttar Pradesh]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of India|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Balrampur district|Balrampur]]\n| established_title       = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| government_type         = Parliamentary Seat \n| governing_body          = Shravasti\n| unit_pref               = Metric\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_rank               = \n| area_total_km2          =\n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = \n| population_total       = \n| population_as_of        = \n| population_rank         =